title: Talking Markets with RBC's Lori Calvasina
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin, deputy editor Ben Levisohn and RBC Capital Markets' managing director Lori Calvasina discuss the outlook for financial markets, industry sectors, and individual stocks.
